title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 05.20.08
description:
TEENAGE TOUGH GIRL?
    -------------------
    Talk about a problem child! Ariel, a 14-year-old girl, emotionally and physically abuses her mother, Linda. Ariel has punched and choked Linda, and even makes fun of her disabled brother! She claims that if she ever had a baby and it cried she would "shake it to death!!" She also likes to brag about her sexual endeavors with over 30 men, some of who are over 30 years old!!!! Watch Steve break Ariel down as he tries to figure out why she&#039;s so abusive and slutty! Will Ariel and her mother kiss and make-up, or will we see yet another family brawl?!

ENJOY PLEASE SEED AND SAY THANK YOU
